SUMMARY:Deadline: Eliza Moore Fellowship for Artistic Excellence 2026 (Oak 
 Spring)
DESCRIPTION:Eliza Moore Fellowship for Artistic Excellence from the Oak Spr
 ing Garden Foundation\, supporting early-career artists whose work engages
  plants\, gardens and landscapes. ELIGIBILITY: early-career visual and lit
 erary artists\, dancers and musicians\; no nationality restriction stated\
 , though the residency takes place on site in Virginia. Apply via the Oak 
 Spring fellowships page.\n\nOrganisation: Oak Spring Garden Foundation\nLo
 cation: Upperville\, Virginia\, USA (2-5 week on-site residency)\nAward: $
 10\,000 grant plus a two- to five-week residency with accommodation provid
 ed. No application fee.\nDuration: Two- to five-week residency\n\nMore: ht
 tps://www.osgf.org/fellowships/eliza-moore-artistic-excellence
URL:https://www.osgf.org/fellowships/eliza-moore-artistic-excellence
LOCATION:Upperville\, Virginia\, USA (2-5 week on-site residency)
